REPOSITORY YANG SUDAH ADA ISINYA
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Step | Command / Aksi                     | Keterangan                                         |
| ---- | ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| 1    | Buat/Edit `.gitignore`             | Tambahkan file/folder yang ingin di-ignore         |
| 2    | `git rm -r --cached namafolder`    | Hapus tracking Git jika file sudah terlanjur masuk |
| 3    | `git add .`                        | Refresh staging                                    |
| 4    | `git commit -m "update gitignore"` | Simpan perubahan                                   |
| 5    | `git push`                         | Upload perubahan                                   |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CONTOH HAPUS TRACKING
| Kasus                        | Command                    |
| ---------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Hapus tracking folder `bin`  | `git rm -r --cached bin`   |
| Hapus tracking folder `.vs`  | `git rm -r --cached .vs`   |
| Hapus tracking file tertentu | `git rm --cached namafile` |

